{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_63","type":"agent_message","text":"The remaining error on `java.lang.Object()` is clearly coming from the test-side serialization helper, so I’m tightening that condition to the test class instead of the library class. For `EnhancedThrowableRenderer`, I’m switching from only making the image loader see the class to also exposing the class file as a resource so the isolated `URLClassLoader` can load its own copy and exercise the intended fallback path."}}
